+<a name="headers"></a>
+### .headers(object)
+Sets all the keys of the object as response headers. [`.header`](#headerkey-value) will be called under the hood.
+```js
+reply.headers({
+  'x-foo': 'foo',
+  'x-bar': 'bar'
+})
+```
